To apply for this position, you must provide a complete application package by 11:59 PM (EST) on 10/29/2021. Application packages MUST include:
1. Cover Letter;
2. Resume or Curriculum Vitae submitted in any format that supports the Knowledge, Skills and Abilities described in this announcement;
3. Academic Transcripts;
4. Three (3) Letters of Recommendation;
5. DD-214, if claiming veteran's preference;
6. Statement of service from your unit, if currently serving on active duty; and,
7. Copy of Sponsor's Permanent Change of Station orders and marriage certificate, if claiming military spouse preference. In order to receive full consideration, applications should be postmarked or received by the closing date of the announcement. Due to COVID -19 restrictions, only electronic applications will be accepted at this time. please submit your full application package to: Mrs. Mrs. Rose Maresco
Email: rose.maresco@westpoint.edu

